{"tid":298601,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"The Mist.霧地異煞電視被討論區","createTime":"2017-06-26T12:00:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-23T12:53:37.000Z","uid":46575,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0a78afc82524114e7eb575725830af9bf1d53d29","tid":298601,"uid":46575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T12:00:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/26/195448_a3ef0665322db8b2e3785411eb1d7e34.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F26%2F195448_a3ef0665322db8b2e3785411eb1d7e34.jpg&h=f4abb060&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n電影版劇情緊湊，但其實劇情仍然有發展空間，因此美劇版仍很值得期待。美劇版《The Mist》由Spike推出，會有10集，於6月22日首播！<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/26/195611_564fa1dac54da6db2558fd6d5f344c12.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F26%2F195611_564fa1dac54da6db2558fd6d5f344c12.jpg&h=ed0ed7f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n從預告中可以看到，美劇版的主要場景變成了是整個商場，另外亦有教堂，空間比電影版的超級市場大得多，劇情亦可以有更多發揮<br />\n<br />\n電視版預告<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kya_uqiSQOY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dkya_uqiSQOY&d=sILGtb%2BDMmnLl%2FYA%2Bpb3YARJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=ef4ff320\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kya_uqiSQOY</a><br />\n<br />\n暫時今日去到第3集<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfc464946620ccb20f259f0f7e0c8c419a08217d","tid":298601,"uid":7711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T12:03:32.000Z","msg":"評價好似麻麻"},{"pid":"1894689e10ba284401f3f87bc9886f1ceb35a3a6","tid":298601,"uid":46575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T12:10:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>評價好似麻麻</blockquote><br />\n第一集舖排人物角色關系有小小悶<br />\n之後好番小小"},{"pid":"4a7cdd9803e05e3caca589d4eb4264c8150a4188","tid":298601,"uid":74244,"like":0,"dis